Maple Terroir Maple Syrup Dark Chocolate Roasted Almonds

"
					
						Maple Terroir is one of the most recognized maple brands in Canada. Adding to their fine collection of high-quality maple related products, this unique double-roasted, non-GMO almonds dipped in pure maple syrup and dark chocolate, then coated with 70% cocoa. This remarkable blend offers a rich chocolate taste, light crunchy bite, with a subtle maple flavour.
Features:
18 individual bags in a gift box
1.8 kg (4 lb.) total
12-month shelf-life in a cool place
Canadian grown, Canadian made


"
